quote: Comparative segmentation results on the Synapse dataset.
The proposed method for medical image segmentation was validated through experiments on two tasks.
Given the trade-off between accuracy and speed, we choose to utilize the tiny-based architecture for medical image segmentation.
Our results show that incorporating more skip-connections leads to improved performance.
Swin-unet: Unet-like pure transformer for medical image segmentation.
U-net transformer: Self and cross attention for medical image segmentation.
